<p><em><strong>Source:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/global-development/2026/mar/30/urgent-action-needed-to-prevent-surge-in-digital-violence-in-africa-experts-say\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Guardian</a></em></p>

