<p><em><strong>Source:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/world/2026/mar/26/sudan-drone-strikes-civilian-targets-north-darfur-market-north-kordofan-truck\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Guardian</a></em></p>

