<p><em><strong>Source:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/news/2026/mar/26/nigeria-regional-superpower-uk-reparative-justice-trade-economic-ties\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Guardian</a></em></p>

