<p><em><strong>Source:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/culture/2026/mar/25/ebo-m-lion-king-circle-of-life-chant-learnmore-jonasi-lawsuit\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Guardian</a></em></p>
