<p><em><strong>Source:</strong> <a href=\"https://www.theguardian.com/news/2026/mar/25/un-votes-slave-trade-gravest-crime-against-humanity-reparatory-justice\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">The Guardian</a></em></p>
